Bridgewalker is a euro-denominated wallet for Android. It allows sending and receiving of bitcoins, but does so by exchanging back and forth to Euros on the fly.

Feature Overview:

* Send and receive Bitcoins using QR codes or Bitcoin URIs
* Sharing of Bitcoin address via standard Android share function
* Support for [[green addresses|Green_address]]
* One-click registration

This project was announced on March 23, 2013 (1.1).

